{"tid":2362971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國助理國務卿接見台灣駐美代表蕭美琴 響應日前蓬佩奧解除美台交流限制 美國駐荷蘭大使亦於大使館內接見台灣駐荷代表","createTime":"2021-01-12T00:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T03:50:48.000Z","uid":292499,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"50992a271f17c548298c22515ab7e7adef8eceb6","tid":2362971,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:40:23.000Z","msg":"美國國務院9日才宣布取消美台交往限制，今天就高調透過「每日行程公告」，公布國務院政軍局助理國務卿古柏（Clarke Cooper）將於美東時間11日上午11時30分（台灣時間12日凌晨零時30分）與蕭美琴進行閉門會晤，但未公布兩人會面地點。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）9日發聲明宣布，美國國務院即起取消內部所有與台灣往來施加的自我限制。美國駐荷蘭大使胡克斯特拉（Pete Hoekstra）用行動響應，邀請我國駐荷蘭代表陳欣新會面。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202101120016.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202101120016.aspx&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=cd450f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202101120016.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3408248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3408248&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=9c0a0f04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3408248&h=5149b6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3408248</a>"},{"pid":"badf302eb06c11861a977f7eaf9f6808a0df4a13","tid":2362971,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重大突破"},{"pid":"533226d606e1a6560f2528837369aabfa73c174a","tid":2362971,"uid":204565,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedB